带有大量注释的vimrc文件，可当做一个tutorial.

使用：

git clone https://github.com/gaopenghigh/vimrc
cp vimrc ~/.vimrc
mkdir -p ~/.vim/bundle
git clone https://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git ~/.vim/bundle/vundle
cd ~/.vim/bundle && git clone https://github.com/Lokaltog/vim-powerline
cd ~/.vim/bundle && git clone https://github.com/jnwhiteh/vim-golang.git
cd ~/.vim/bundle && git clone https://github.com/scrooloose/nerdtree.git
cd ~/.vim/bundle && git clone https://github.com/tomasr/molokai

打开vim, 输入:

:PluginInstall
    
来安装插件! Enjoy!
